wiki.summary: “Armed & Dangerous” is about Juice’s lifestyle of wealth, drugs and guns and him reflecting upon his superiority to others after becoming famous. This marks the first collaboration between Juice and Dre Moon. The song was performed at concerts in Copenhagen and Amsterdam on the JUICEWRLD: The World Domination Tour. Clips from the concert are also included in the music video. In March, 2019, it was also added to his debut album, Goodbye and Good Riddance. :0 Read more on Last.fm.
